OL,3,CHundreds of anti-GST protestors gather
OL,4,Coutside Guernsey States
OL,6,FGuernsey Deputies had to make their
OL,7,Fway through hundreds of protestors on
OL,8,FWednesday morning for the start of a
OL,9,Fdebate which could see a goods and
OL,10,Fservices tax introduced.
OL,12,FPoliticians have to decide whether to
OL,13,Faccept Policy and Resources (P&R) tax
OL,14,Fplan, which includes a 3% GST, plus
OL,15,Fchanges to income tax and social
OL,16,Fsecurity to soften the blow on poorer
OL,17,Fhouseholds.
OL,19,FHowever, it faces a raft of amendments
OL,20,Fthat range from changing it to binning
OL,21,Fit entirely.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
