PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784231285
OL,3,CHundreds of anti-GST protestors gather
OL,4,Coutside Guernsey States
OL,6,FThe detractors made their feelings
OL,7,Ffelt in force on Wednesday morning,
OL,8,Fgathering outside by the States steps
OL,9,Fin St Peter Port to demand that GST is
OL,10,Fdumped.
OL,12,FOne of those keen to make their views
OL,13,Fheard, Karen, spoke directly with the
OL,14,FPresident of P&R - Deputy Lindsay de
OL,15,FSausmarez.
OL,17,FShe explains: "I'm down here today
OL,18,Fbecause this island is extortionate
OL,19,Fenough. We do not need GST. I'm one of
OL,20,Fthe people on the bread line and I'm
OL,21,Fbarely getting by in life.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784231285
OL,3,CHundreds of anti-GST protestors gather
OL,4,Coutside Guernsey States
OL,6,F"I had to sell my house ... and
OL,7,Fthey're squeezing more and more taxes
OL,8,Fout of people. Everybody is just going
OL,9,Fto be leaving this island."
OL,11,FIt comes as Deputy de Sausmarez
OL,12,Fadmitted that the Committee's plans
OL,13,Faren't popular and politicians aren't
OL,14,Fvoted in to make popular choices, but
OL,15,Fones that benefit the island.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784231285
OL,3,CHundreds of anti-GST protestors gather
OL,4,Coutside Guernsey States
OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "Our job is
OL,7,Fliterally to make decisions based on
OL,8,Fthe information that we have available
OL,9,Fto us. A big part of what our job is,
OL,10,Fis to make sure that we do have the
OL,11,Fright information so we can make well-
OL,12,Finformed and evidence-based decisions.
OL,14,F"We need more in the way of healthcare
OL,15,Fand social care ... pensions. People
OL,16,Fdo recognise the fact that our current
OL,17,Fsystem isn't sustainable and we do
OL,18,Fneed to do something about it.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
