PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784231285
OL,3,CHundreds of anti-GST protestors gather
OL,4,Coutside Guernsey States
OL,6,F"(Our proposals) bring money in from
OL,7,Fcorporates, from visitors and from the
OL,8,Fwealthiest residents in the island,
OL,9,Fand actually makes sure that the
OL,10,Fdisproportionate benefit goes to
OL,11,Fpeople on average or lower incomes."
OL,13,FThe plans sit don't sit well with
OL,14,Fprotestors, as Karen adds: "I think
OL,15,Fthey're out for themselves. They just
OL,16,Fcare about themselves.
OL,18,F"They don't care about the general
OL,19,Fpublic and the community. They want to
OL,20,Fsqueeze every last thing they can out
OL,21,Fof us."
OL,26,@nD@BpmnD@Ppn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
