PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784231285
OL,3,CHundreds of anti-GST protestors gather
OL,4,Coutside Guernsey States
OL,6,FThe island's most senior committee is
OL,7,Fproposing its tax plan to plug what
OL,8,Fthey say is an ongoing estimated
OL,9,Ffunding gap of #50 million.
OL,11,FBut its reasoning has been heavily
OL,12,Fcriticised, with detractors arguing
OL,13,Fthat the island's financial position
OL,14,Fmight not be as bad as P&R says it is.
OL,16,FSeveral multi-million pound failed
OL,17,Fgovernment projects have been cited as
OL,18,Freasons why people don't trust the
OL,19,FGovernment with their money.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784231285
OL,3,CHundreds of anti-GST protestors gather
OL,4,Coutside Guernsey States
OL,6,F"We don't need an additional tax
OL,7,Fsystem," one person told ITV Channel.
OL,9,F"You need to sort the spending out
OL,10,Ffirst, any business would know that,
OL,11,Feverybody here more or less knows
OL,12,Fthat."
OL,14,FThe criticism hasn't just been in
OL,15,Fperson, politicians say they've been
OL,16,Fbombarded with hundreds of emails from
OL,17,Fthe public overnight, 90% of which are
OL,18,Fanti-GST.
OL,20,FDeputy Garry Collins says he's
OL,21,Freceived about 700 emails so far.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784231285
OL,3,CHundreds of anti-GST protestors gather
OL,4,Coutside Guernsey States
OL,6,FHe explains: "Personally, I am very
OL,7,Fgrateful for the messages and reading
OL,8,Fthe stories helped me understand why
OL,9,Fthey had chosen to email.
OL,11,F"About 400 were a simple, no to GST,
OL,12,For a little more than that, but about
OL,13,F300 had real stories, struggling
OL,14,Ffamilies, pensioners on reduced
OL,15,Fpensions, people already about to
OL,16,Fleave the Island as the cost of living
OL,17,Fis too much."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
