OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784231285
OL,3,CHundreds of anti-GST protestors gather
OL,4,Coutside Guernsey States
OL,6,FThere will be 22 amendments to P&R's
OL,7,Fplan for GST, and one attempt to pause
OL,8,Fit until the island's tax backlog is
OL,9,Fsorted out.
OL,11,FThe debate is expected to last for the
OL,12,Fnext three days.
OL,14,FIf P&R is unsuccessful, a motion of no
OL,15,Fconfidence in the top committee has
OL,16,Falready been announced by opposing
OL,17,Fpoliticians.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/9
